ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectAgreement for the Sharing of Visa and Immigration Information
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to sign, or to delegate powers to sign, on behalf of Canada, subject to ratification, the AGREEMENT between the Government of Canada and the Government of the UNITED STATES OF AMERICA FOR THE SHARING OF VISA AND IMMIGRATION INFORMATION.
